# ACU Lifecycle

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RawExport
    RawExport --> Parser: Provider Import
    Parser --> Normalize: Transform to ACU
    Normalize --> Encrypt: Per-ACU Key
    Encrypt --> Sign: Identity Key
    Sign --> Store: Vault Write
    Store --> Search: Index
    Store --> Classify: Rights Detection
    Classify --> Consent: Assign Tier
    Consent --> Export: User Action
    Export --> Marketplace: For Sale
    Export --> [*]
    
    state Parser {
        [*] --> IdentifyProvider
        IdentifyProvider --> ExtractFields
        ExtractFields --> ValidateSchema
        ValidateSchema --> [*]
    }
    
    state Encrypt {
        [*] --> DeriveACK
        DeriveACK --> DeriveNonce
        DeriveNonce --> XChaCha20Poly1305
        XChaCha20Poly1305 --> [*]
    }